data.name: label105.Text
data.value: Resin, which has a lower Dk and higher Df than e-glass, will fill the gaps between traces. Initial values come from program settings. Consult your laminate manufacturer for actual resin Dk and Df. (To estimate resin Dk and Dfr, use Dkr~0.8 x Dk-prepreg and Dfr~1.5 x Df-prepreg.)

data.name: label96.Text
data.value: Laminate-side roughness (Rz1) is controlled by the laminate manufacturer. Prepreg-side roughness (Rz2) is determined by the oxide treatment used by the PCB manufacturer. (Range: 0.5 - 15 um)
